— W USA (foothills on E edge of the Sacramento Valley, N 
<taxonomicName id="73944D33876CB1361AF55A28FDAAF3AE" box="[428,574,3130,3155]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Geraniaceae" genus="California" kingdom="Plantae" order="Geraniales" pageId="35" pageNumber="228" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">California</taxonomicName>
).
